# 🔐 Cybersecurity Mentor Bot
A friendly, practical AI mentor that guides aspiring cybersecurity 
professionals step by step — from beginner concepts to career-ready skills.

## 🎯 Who It's For
Anyone looking to break into cybersecurity, level up their skills, 
or get guided career advice from an AI mentor.

## ✨ Features
- Step-by-step cybersecurity career guidance
- Beginner-friendly explanations of security concepts
- Practical, actionable career advice
- Friendly and approachable conversational tone
- Covers tools, certifications, and job prep

